%body#services
  = haml :'layout/navbar_static'
  #grid-first
    .container
      .row.header
        %h3 Syme takes your privacy seriously.
        %p
          We use state-of-the-art encryption technology to protect your data.
      .row.sections
        .col-md-4
          .section
            .pic
              %img.img-responsive{:alt => "services2", :src => "images/services2.png"}
            .info
              %strong SSL with forward secrecy
              %p
                All connections to our service are encrypted using SSL/TLS with perfect forward secrecy (PFF) enabled. Our SSL setup has an A+ quality rating according to the
                %a{href: 'https://www.ssllabs.com/ssltest/analyze.html?d=getsyme.com'}
                  Qualys SSL Labs.
                
        .col-md-4
          .section
            .pic
              %img.img-responsive{:alt => "services4", :src => "images/services4.png"}
            .info
              %strong AES-256 and ECC-256
              %p
                Your data is encrypted with the same industry-standard encryption primitives used by Bitcoin to protect electronic transactions. 
        .col-md-4
          .section
            .pic
              %img.img-responsive{:alt => "services3", :src => "images/services3.png"}
            .info
              %strong Trusted code delivery
              %p
                Syme is delivered as an extension and runs in a secure sandbox away from potentially malicious web pages.
