              %p Syme uses PBKDF2 with 10,000 iterations of HMAC-SHA256 to increase protection against weak passwords.
        .col-md-6.feature
          %img{:alt => "location", :src => "images/circle-icons/full-color/location.png"}
            .info
              %strong Secure authentication
              %p Users are authenticated with the Secure Remote Password protocol (SRP). Passwords are never sent across the network.
